            . The prosecutor deposed to the note, he said he did not take notice of the number, but was certain as to the letter.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17750218-67-person578">
                  Wallace
                   Larkin
               <interp inst="t17750218-67-person578" type="surname" value="Larkin"></interp>
